"इति"

#. Tag: emphasis
#: configuration-files.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid "foo.keymap"
msgstr "foo.keymap इति"

#. Tag: para
#: configuration-files.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a <literal role=\"extension\">.ini</literal> file that holds a <link "
"linkend=\"configure-shortcuts\">Key binding profile</link>. Until "
"&krusader;-1.70.0 this was a binary file. &krusader; is backwards compatible "
"for importing this legacy binary format."
msgstr ""
"इति क<literal role=\"extension\"> .इनि</literal> सञ्चिका या धारयति a<link "
"linkend=\"configure-shortcuts\"> कुंजी बन्धन प्रोफाइल</link> . &amp;"
"krusader;-1.70.0 पर्यन्तं एषा द्विचक्रीयसञ्चिका आसीत् । &amp;krusader; अस्य विरासतां "
"द्विचक्रीयस्वरूपस्य आयातार्थं पश्चात्तापसङ्गतम् अस्ति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: configuration-files.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid "Location: <filename> /usr/share/krusader/foo.keymap</filename>"
msgstr "स्थानम् : <filename> /usr/share/krusader/foo.keymap</filename> इति"

#. Tag: emphasis
#: configuration-files.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid "foo.color"
msgstr "फू.रङ्गः"

#. Tag: para
#: configuration-files.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a binary file that holds the <link linkend=\"konfig-color\">Color "
"Scheme</link>."
msgstr ""
"इयं द्विचक्रीयसञ्चिका अस्ति या धारयति<link linkend=\"konfig-color\"> रङ्ग योजना</"
"link> ."

#. Tag: para
#: configuration-files.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid "Location: <filename>/usr/share/krusader/foo.color</filename>"
msgstr "स्थानम् : <filename>/usr/share/krusader/foo.color</filename> इति"
